好<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150717/19222665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150717%2F19222665&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=7dde9c0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150717%2F19222665&h=cba730c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150717/19222665</a><br />\n<br />\n今年5月才因於2011年強姦酒吧女經理，而被重囚18年的印度籍青年，昨承認干犯另一強姦案，案中女事主為一名內地女大學生，於2013年入住重慶大廈的旅館。女生洗澡後以毛巾包裹身體在房內講電話，印度男突然衝入房，稱希望一睹事主胴體。女生驚惶失措，以為讓對方望一眼便可了事，加上擔心被殺，便同意讓印度男撫摸，詎料對方將她強姦。<br />\n記者：黃幗慧<br />\n<br />\n印度籍男被告Mohammad Farhan Azad（28歲），昨於高等法院承認一項強姦罪，辯方將於今日求情。法官曾建議索閱女事主X的創傷報告，惟因原於英國留學的X不願再留港而告吹。<br />\n案發時22歲的X與女友人在2013年來港旅遊，於6月1日入住重慶大廈13樓的萊茵迎賓館一晚。由於旅館不設私人浴室，X與友人分別到走廊的公眾浴室洗澡。"},{"pid":"aea7bd15d1a3ffbcea25da8f06c200c1096bf01d","tid":1915552,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"玩撚完"},{"pid":"bf9971da3053d8f3421d6ca9f5604b26ea75c51f","tid":1915552,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"幾千個家居隔離<br />\n1% 都夠死啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfc7d3c303150ea637cd2112c184b8a06503408","tid":1915552,"uid":237222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0cacaae74fdc567c008fc1481f312d7b6d6c1f21","tid":1915552,"uid":32527,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"呢度唔比做隔離營 個度又唔比<br />\n咪大家攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要大大方方咁比錢維權  唔通洗錢包起幾棟酒店隔離?<br />\n        <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊係慳埋呢筆  佛系抗疫"},{"pid":"8fbff19e51bd9b2f1369db31b0a2fbcadf881a52",